snippet.title: THRONE AND LIBERTY - Welcome to Solisium | Launch Date Reveal
snippet.description:
Claim the throne and shape the future of Solisium. Launching on Steam (PC), PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, on September 17. Learn More:  PlayThroneandLiberty.com

Play the Open Beta on July 18 - 23.

THRONE AND LIBERTY is a cross-platform,  guild-focused, MMORPG where you battle malevolent enemies and harness ancient powers to protect Solisium. Explore a dynamic open world, customize your character, and wield a diverse arsenal of weapons. Shapeshift into creatures and engage in epic battles. Join PvP combat, castle sieges, and dungeons. 

STEAM – https://bit.ly/3ScIrh5
SONY – https://bit.ly/4bIFVWT
MICROSOFT – https://bit.ly/3XZZDu5

FOLLOW US ON SOCIAL 
X:  https://twitter.com/playtlgame 
Instagram:  https://www.instagram.com/playthroneandliberty 
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/playthroneandliberty
